nodes.text: The Webweaver caverns was an underground cavern found beneath the Nawataa Waterfall in the Kkowir Forest on the planet Kashyyyk. The cavern was infested by spiders.

The Webweaver caverns first appeared in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
